# A5: per-step-mutated planning state is LOCAL (generated views), never committed.
# Only increments/ and releases/ are the durable, committed source of truth —
# so two people on two branches never conflict on the planning files.
STATE.md
tracking.json
.cursor.json
.state.lock
.state.journal
.backup/
migration-manifest.json
# Performance-audit telemetry buffer. Holds the engineer's real prompt samples
# until clock-out — must NEVER be committed (raw prompt text, may contain PII).
.session-usage.json
